JOCS - Javascript Opensource Comment System

A comment system in javascript like a very small disqus.

written with angularjs.

Need a REST backend.
Default one is pocs written in php with silex.

To install:

    git clone
    grunt

Take the content of the new `dist` repository, this is the compressed app.


